REQUIREMENTS:

ASCIImui requires 'MCC_Urltext'. (Install the 'Urltext.mcc' and 'Urltext.mcp' files,
without them you will recieve a "Cannot create application!" error message).

Urltext.mcc is copyright Alfonso Ranieri <alforan@tin.it>  Thanks!
It's available on Aminet or you can find the latest version at:

http://digilander.libero.it/asoft/

ASCIImui requires OpenURL to process the hyperlinks
